title: Rubi Rose on Getting Signed, dating Playboi Carti, Young Thug drama
description:
Rapper, model, and video vixen Rubi Rose came through the studio to talk about her recent signing to LA Reid, her past relationship with Playboi Carti, drama with Young Thug, and much more in her first No Jumper interview with Adam22!
